<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>修改项目</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/bootstrap.css'/>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css'/>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/jquery.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/web/">首页</a> |
        <a href="/web/project/<%=project.name%>/show">项目首页</a> |
    </nav>

    <%if(msg){%>
    <div class="alert alert-<%if(error){%>danger<%}else{%>success<%}%> tip i-hide"><%=msg%></div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $('.tip').show().delay(2000).fadeOut();
    </script>
    <%}%>
    <form method="POST" class="form-horizontal" role="form">
        <fieldset>
            <div class="item form-group">
                <label class="long col-sm-2 control-label">项目名</label>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                    <%=project.name%>
                    <input type="hidden" name="name" value="<%=project.name%>" class="form-control">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item form-group">
                <label class="long col-sm-2 control-label">描述</label>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                    <input type="text" name="des" required="" value="<%=project.des%>" class="form-control">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item form-group">
                <label class="long col-sm-2 control-label">项目负责人</label>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                    <input type="text" name="owner" required="" value="<%=project.owner%>" class="form-control">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item form-group">
                <label class="long col-sm-2 control-label">打包默认的命名空间</label>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                    <input type="text" name="namespace" required="" value="<%=project.namespace%>" class="form-control">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item form-group">
                <label class="long col-sm-2 control-label">是否有上crowdin平台</label>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                    <select class="form-control" name="crowdin">
                        <option value="0" <%if(project.crowdin=='0'){%>selected<%}%> >无</option>
                        <option value="1" <%if(project.crowdin=='1'){%>selected<%}%> >有</option>
                    </select>
                    <span class="label label-info">*如果上平台，将不允许对英语之外的其他语言进行修改</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item form-group">
                <label class="long col-sm-2 control-label">语言模式是否有带id</label>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                    <select class="form-control" name="hasId">
                        <option value="1" <%if(project.hasId=='1'){%>selected<%}%> >有</option>
                        <option value="0" <%if(project.hasId=='0'){%>selected<%}%> >无</option>
                    </select>
                    <span class="label label-info">*平台上的语言模式，有些项目在crowdin上面是用id作为key(比如web.airdroid.com)，这时候就要带id, 有些项目是用key作为key的(比如手机端)，这时候就不用带id</span>
                    <span class="label label-info">*如果不带id的话，默认的csv格式只有3列，即 key value context, 导出上平台csv和导入翻译结果的时候，都要只有3行</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item form-group">
                <label class="long col-sm-2 control-label">crowdin 平台对应的项目文件名称</label>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                    <input type="text" name="package" required="" value="<%=project.package || project.name%>" class="form-control">
                    <sapn class="label label-info">*上平台才有效,该名称要与crowdin的名称一样，不然导入翻译结果的时候会出错</sapn>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
                    <input type="submit" value="提交" class="btn btn-primary">
                </div>
            </div>
        </fieldset>
    </form>
</div>
</body>
</html>